guy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Thu-Ph%E1%BB%91-k%C3%BD-n%E1%BB%99i/poem-4J24Ky09PgBh1BHDh7F7MQ">Thu Phố ký nội - 秋浦寄內</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1-M%E1%BB%99-xu%C3%A2n-tam-nguy%E1%BB%87t-Vu-Gi%C3%A1p-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-sQhNXURAoPbnienA1rpcPQ">Tức sự (Mộ xuân tam nguyệt Vu Giáp trường) - 即事（暮春三月巫峽長）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/%E1%BB%A8c-giang-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Ng%C3%B4-x%E1%BB%AD-s%C4%A9/poem-BpmzAGJvrymZfyytily7-w">Ức giang thượng Ngô xử sĩ - 憶江上吳處士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/author-zlEhGhvit8FPpDIsa8T0QA">Giả Đảo</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
